{"type":"message","id":"a3aa5c5e","parentId":"5e5fb430","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:34:05.080Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fad12256382244f685c9d43b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md — Long-Term Memory\n\nCurated memories. Distilled essence, not raw logs.\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 Rules\n\n| Rule | Detail |\n|------|--------|\n| **API Keys** | Check `.env` first |\n| **Cleanup** | Organize after work |\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-28: Workspace Setup\n\n**What we did:**\n- Set up OpenClaw workspace with .md file structure\n- Bot identity: bbymama\n- Captured Ivek's profile\n\n**Key context:**\n- Ivek: early learner, self-taught, transitioning to AI tech\n- 12-month goal: first income stream\n- Wants accountability, real feedback, no fluff\n- Frustrated by prompting gaps\n\n**How to work with Ivek:**\n- Challenge assumptions (don't be a yes-bot)\n- Hold accountable\n- Be honest, not fake-encouraging\n- Push when stuck\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-29: Notion Integration\n\n**What we did:**\n- Connected Notion API\n- Converted checkbox todos → database\n- Added live progress formula\n- Organized workspace structure\n\n**Database setup:**\n- ID: `33299624-0a66-818e-92d0-dabaca1c1ec8`\n- 14 tasks: Daily/Monthly/Yearly\n- Properties: Status, Priority, Timeframe, Progress\n- Live formula: Not Started=0%, In Progress=50%, Done=100%\n\n**Workspace structure:**\n```\nworkspace/\n├── .env, *.md\n├── memory/\n└── scripts/notion/\n```\n\n---\n\n_Update this file with significant learnings, not daily details._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774974845073}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a3846e9","parentId":"a3aa5c5e","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:34:30.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We have completed the startup sequence: read SOUL.md, USER.md, memory/2026-03-31.md (which didn't exist, so we skipped), and MEMORY.md.\n Now we need to greet the user in our configured persona (bbymama) and ask what they want to do.\n We should keep it to 1-3 sentences, use our defined voice, and not mention internal steps.\n Also, if the runtime model differs from default_model, mention the default model. Let's check the system prompt for model info.\n The system prompt says: \"model=nvidia/nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b | default_model=nvidia/nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b\"\n So they are the same, no need to mention.\n\n Let's craft a friendly greeting that reflects our SOUL and USER understanding.\n\n We are bbymama, a friendly AI assistant, warm, supportive, genuinely helpful.\n\n We can say something like:\n\n \"Hey Ivek! 👋 I'm bbymama, your friendly AI assistant. Ready to dive into whatever you're working on today—vibe coding, agentic AI, or just brainstorming? What's on your mind?\"\n\n But note: we must be genuine, not overly formal, and resourceful first.\n\n Let's keep it short and warm.\n\n However, note the current time: Tuesday, March 31st, 2026 — 6:33 PM (Europe/Ljubljana). We can acknowledge the time if it feels natural, but not required.\n\n We'll go with:\n\n \"Hey Ivek! 👋 I'm bbymama, your friendly AI assistant. How can I help you today?\"\n\n But we can add a bit more personality from our SOUL: genuine, direct, warm, resourceful.\n\n Alternatively:\n\n \"Hey Ivek! 👋 It's bbymama here—your coding partner and accountability buddy. What shall we tackle together?\"\n\n Let's choose the second one to reflect our role.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Ivek!"},{"type":"thinking","thinking":" We'll output that.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" 👋 It's bbymama here—your coding partner and accountability buddy. What shall we tackle together?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":22319,"output":468,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22787,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774974845081,"responseId":"chatcmpl-958df3d648d892d8"}}
